data.description: Stunning west side home, quiet community, corner lot with nice finishes and features, ready for your family to enjoy! This home has it all with 3 large bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a flex space/loft and lovely curb appeal. The great room is impressive with custom shelving and lighting, tall ceilings plenty of spacing for all of your furniture. The kitchen is open to the dining and back with peninsula breakfast bar, stainless steel appliance package and good natural light. All bedrooms are available together upstairs with that additional flex spacing that everyone needs, perfect for a home office for those working from home or extra space for the kids. Main bedroom suite is large and spacious, with en suite bath containing jetted tub, separate shower, large vanity and closet. This home sits on a large corner lot at the end of a cul de sac, 100% landscaped from and back, very quiet neighborhood. Location is a 10 out of 10 with quick access to I-10, west side outlet mall, shopping and outstanding schools.
